-- Kavo UI Library (Optimized)
-- Changes from original:
--   1. Replaced all `while wait() do` theme polling loops with a single
--      centralized RunService.Heartbeat theme-sync system.
--   2. Extracted the repeated ripple/sample animation into a shared helper.
--   3. Extracted the repeated viewInfo tooltip logic into a shared helper.
--   4. Extracted the repeated hover-highlight logic into a shared helper.
--   5. Replaced the long if/elseif chain for theme lookup with a table index.
--   6. Replaced `Kavo:ToggleUI` boolean branch with a simple `not` toggle.
--   7. Localised `game.TweenService` once at the top (was repeatedly called as
--      a global `game.TweenService` inside every element).
--   8. Removed the broken `for i,v in pairs(sectionInners:GetChildren()) do
--      while wait() do` loop that could never iterate correctly.
--   9. Removed redundant `wait(0)` calls (no-ops in Roblox).
--  10. Removed `local oldTheme = ""` which was declared but never used.
--  11. Removed the Settings/config pcall block that read/wrote a JSON file but
--      never actually consumed the result anywhere in the library.
--  12. Fixed `mouse.Move:connect` → `:Connect` (deprecated lowercase form).
--  13. Deduplicated the dropdown option builder into a shared `addOption`
--      function so `NewDropdown` and `DropFunction:Refresh` share one path.
--  14. Replaced `Color3.fromRGB(r*255±n, …)` offset arithmetic with a small
--      `shiftColor` helper so the pattern isn't repeated ~30 times.

